---
title: Golden Chicken Schnitzel & Tartare Sauce with Fries & Cucumber Salad
description: Boost the flavour of a classic chicken schnitzel by adding the Aussie spice to the golden crumb coating. Served with
tartare sauce, fries and a crisp salad for a meal nobody can refuse!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
